</div>
<p id="p6">Mann is also <a href="https://www.austinmann.com/trek/iphone-17-pro-camera-review-dolomites" rel="noopener noreferrer">a fan of the new selfie camera</a>, using it to take selfies as he biked through the mountains:</p>
<blockquote id="blockquote7"><p>
  This is one of those features that just works without any effort and will make everyone&rsquo;s selfies better, and many users won&rsquo;t even be aware of what it&rsquo;s doing. Just as I hoped, I can hold the iPhone in horizontal or vertical orientation and the camera automatically adjusts based on whether I&rsquo;m alone or surrounded by others.
</p></blockquote>
<p id="p8">As always, it&rsquo;s worth scrolling through the entire post because the Dolomites are a beautiful mountain range that offered a lot of opportunities for Mann to show off the new iPhone 17 Pro&rsquo;s cameras.</p>
